Welcome to Banyan Rail Services
Banyan Rail Services Inc. (“Banyan”), is a publicly traded company headquartered in Boca Raton, Florida.
Banyan is led by Gary O. Marino, Chairman. Our mission is to grow shareholder value through strategic acquisitions of leading companies within the industrial, energy, transportation and health care industries throughout North America. Our common stock is traded on the Over-the-Counter Bulletin Board under the symbol “BARA” [OTCBB: BARA].
 

 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 


















