About Banyan
Banyan Rail Services Inc. (Banyan) was formed in 1985 and is a publicly held company headquartered in Boca Raton, Florida.
Banyan is actively seeking acquisitions of leading companies within the industrial, energy, transportation, technology and health care industries throughout North America.
We can secure the capital to allow your company to position itself to develop and become an industry leader.

 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 


















